{
  "texts": [
    "It can automatically generate bibliographies and import papers from other research software.",
    "Its AI-powered recommendation engine and collaborative workspace encourage researchers to interact and collaborate easily with peers and other researchers online.",
    "This assists the researcher in finding relevant research articles based on what they are reading.",
    "With the help of Mendeley, researchers can access the papers online.",
    "It provides an opportunity to create a completely individualized database."
  ]
}